com.cyc.baseclient.datatype

Class DataTypeConverter<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.datatype.DataTypeConverter<E>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DateConverter, MoneyConverter, TimeIntervalConverter

    public abstract class DataTypeConverter<E>
extends Object

    DataTypeConverter is an abstract base class for building classes which convert Java datatypes to their corresponding CycL representations and vice versa.
